title: Lf Partner/Friend/Duo
body:
Looking for a support main preferably to level to level 30 and then also play ranked with me. I'm ad main and season 5 finished in dia 4. I made a new acc and started fresh because I had quit for awhile. Please add me in game or leave a comment if interested. Thank you! 

IGN: 8th Syn

replies.body: Im not one to comment my life story on here but Ive sent a friend request :)
Friend request sent. Played in Southeast server and Chinese before. Diamond 5 in S5. Also just started my account here
Will accept when I get home! Hope to play with you soon mate! :)
